{"tid":1887643,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人想免費補中文","createTime":"2020-02-19T16:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T09:26:05.000Z","uid":135725,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"61d4ba023b6203968556eb9f0f5dedd2082e2f2b","tid":1887643,"uid":135725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:26:28.000Z","msg":"話說呢排學校停哂課，自己又無咩野做<br />\n之前同retake朋友傾計，發現佢都溫到好頹，因為佢好擔心個考試安排<br />\n可能你地會因為社會氣氛／學校停課而影響到你地嘅作戰狀態，所以我希望睇下自己有無機會可以幫到下d中學生<br />\n我係dse前個半年先開始比d力了解中文，最後由mock paper 3 升到dse 5。雖然我成績唔係話好驚人，但我諗我都有d心得可以share比你。如果有興趣就pm我/comment啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：閱5 寫5 說5* 綜5*"},{"pid":"33f239a5be2b0ebcbe8d838dbe719f600b2f0ef5","tid":1887643,"uid":212379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7eec0a9cc3256b7fd879e6211b8712ed3d8ddcb","tid":1887643,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea660f4ab1c1611ecae47d5ddeff866718ed06c3","tid":1887643,"uid":202844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"Oral 5** 可以幫手"},{"pid":"a2a2f23e4ad67ad35c938948ad5a115c24c7b05e","tid":1887643,"uid":212436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:39:55.000Z","msg":"寫作 議論文有咩心得"},{"pid":"715f548f119c7d282d0601529d24cd7de417fa40","tid":1887643,"uid":79219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"求卷二第一題既tips<br />\n同埋卷三<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e78589a644632b242d5783e6ed763fce8cc1ed2","tid":1887643,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"有冇tg可以問問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fe4aa64adedbb92b7f35da7c97466879b190f3","tid":1887643,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7eec0a9cc3256b7fd879e6211b8712ed3d8ddcb","tid":1887643,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"啲pt當通識卷二咁拓展就ok"},{"pid":"ff2680b71a47892b906bfa3dce38a79da8ca5c62","tid":1887643,"uid":290260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61d4ba023b6203968556eb9f0f5dedd2082e2f2b","tid":1887643,"uid":135725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:26:28.000Z","msg":"話說呢排學校停哂課，自己又無咩野做<br />\n之前同retake朋友傾計，發現佢都溫到好頹，因為佢好擔心個考試安排<br />\n可能你地會因為社會氣氛／學校停課而影響到你地嘅作戰狀態，所以我希望睇下自己有無機會可以幫到下d中學生<br />\n我係dse前個半年先開始比d力了解中文，最後由mock paper 3 升到dse 5。雖然我成績唔係話好驚人，但我諗我都有d心得可以share比你。如果有興趣就pm我/comment啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：閱5 寫5 說5* 綜5*"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:43:59.000Z","msg":"F5 中文未合格過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />特別係作文，點寫都係得3x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2005cdfc1ef9375ccda6d8b311d14fe60a6efbe6","tid":1887643,"uid":306701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:45:48.000Z","msg":"我綜合5** 可以幫手"},{"pid":"18fc1f73213aa7f5ab837d6533f4500a91f61ef7","tid":1887643,"uid":103936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:51:15.000Z","msg":"小弟CE 作文5*<br />\n有幾個重點想分享<br />\n1) 練多D修辭手法, 最好試下一篇文用到90%你識嘅修辭<br />\n小弟尤其中意用 比喻 排比 頂真<br />\n好處係好似痾屎咁 出到個頭就自然出埋個尾<br />\n2) 用多D冷門標點, 輔助令你句子結構唔會太死板<br />\n3) 平時功課/操卷, 寫一篇舒情文, <br />\n試一次花極長時間去寫, <br />\n首先真係醞釀個感情, 然後盡力誇張地描寫個畫面<br />\n最後冷靜落黎, 謄一次文, 執執D用字/修辭, 有能力就delete走冗長部份<br />\n<br />\n以上少少個人經驗, 唔次會唔會outdated <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d921270f84551cc3b33eae2f6b453217c8e8878","tid":1887643,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0fe4aa64adedbb92b7f35da7c97466879b190f3","tid":1887643,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7eec0a9cc3256b7fd879e6211b8712ed3d8ddcb","tid":1887643,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"啲pt當通識卷二咁拓展就ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010fe69888126bb935157dbb0eecd48be000ddc5","tid":1887643,"uid":240629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"Sba六十幾 點升5"},{"pid":"1c5c583443391b2efd5e4ccba96afb7bed931024","tid":1887643,"uid":135725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7eec0a9cc3256b7fd879e6211b8712ed3d8ddcb","tid":1887643,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"如果你只係唔識綜合，咁恭喜你，因為綜合係最易捉到路<br />\n第一件事係要練手速，綜合講嘅係資料綜合同分析，你無返咁上下字數都好難完整交代你個Logic flow。就算當年手速慢如我，都起碼寫到5版紙。<br />\n第二件事係logic。聽落好似好易，但其實唔係人人都可以話到比個考官聽你點樣由A跳到B。平時寫Pt個時，諗下中間係咪有d step漏左<br />\n第三件事係中國文化，其實4份卷都涉及到中國文化，如果你可以以中國文化角度去補充論點，咁樣會係一個好好嘅bonus<br />\n<br />\n可能上面有D抽象，我返到屋企再同大家補充例子黎說明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望其他巴打都些牙下佢地嘅經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd23c37640639015fb294667047cc4e528120072","tid":1887643,"uid":121196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:41:43.000Z","msg":"21/2/2020(五)<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">元朗</sp