:204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"有冇tg可以問問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"Tg: kingsleyyyy<br />\n除左問問題，我得閒個時都可以同大家skype分享下經驗，如果有需要就搵我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398cb550b4c8d3fd05eb3826ae7c4f16dc8e7b57","tid":1887643,"uid":135725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d921270f84551cc3b33eae2f6b453217c8e8878","tid":1887643,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0fe4aa64adedbb92b7f35da7c97466879b190f3","tid":1887643,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7eec0a9cc3256b7fd879e6211b8712ed3d8ddcb","tid":1887643,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"啲pt當通識卷二咁拓展就ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:48:48.000Z","msg":"Exact7ly係我以前嘅毛病<br />\n盲點：整合=抄 拓展=自己諗<br />\n但後來我就發現，整合都要自己去補充好多野，個d閱讀資料係比你做個方向/提供一d論點，但中間佢地嘅關係係要由你自己諗"},{"pid":"0ee867042eabfdc627c5b9b3387d42902670b997","tid":1887643,"uid":138489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"中英作文都5** 中文paper 3 5* 想睇卷可以留TG <br />\n就grad唔收補習 唔收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac69c77e45662851e4380e3da5639cfd51d056c4","tid":1887643,"uid":335980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:04:15.000Z","msg":"好有心...支持<br />\n有野都可以幫手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中文 straight A 路過"},{"pid":"a4eb02fa4590748aa662e6e045c1a5b29899c681","tid":1887643,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee867042eabfdc627c5b9b3387d42902670b997","tid":1887643,"uid":138489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"中英作文都5** 中文paper 3 5* 想睇卷可以留TG <br />\n就grad唔收補習 唔收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983a039e03b26a016b613353a3059a14820a2df9","tid":1887643,"uid":135725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c5c583443391b2efd5e4ccba96afb7bed931024","tid":1887643,"uid":135725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7eec0a9cc3256b7fd879e6211b8712ed3d8ddcb","tid":1887643,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"如果你只係唔識綜合，咁恭喜你，因為綜合係最易捉到路<br />\n第一件事係要練手速，綜合講嘅係資料綜合同分析，你無返咁上下字數都好難完整交代你個Logic flow。就算當年手速慢如我，都起碼寫到5版紙。<br />\n第二件事係logic。聽落好似好易，但其實唔係人人都可以話到比個考官聽你點樣由A跳到B。平時寫Pt個時，諗下中間係咪有d step漏左<br />\n第三件事係中國文化，其實4份卷都涉及到中國文化，如果你可以以中國文化角度去補充論點，咁樣會係一個好好嘅bonus<br />\n<br />\n可能上面有D抽象，我返到屋企再同大家補充例子黎說明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望其他巴打都些牙下佢地嘅經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"logic例子說明(詳見2018 p3第三級示例一）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vrrgfma.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVrrgfma.png&h=f148db13&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3P92aUw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3P92aUw.png&h=afede76e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n段落內容：學習的良好態度是熱心發問&rarr;發問是成功學習的關鍵&rarr;扣題（釋囚人士分享）&rarr;指出活動可促進互動的交流&rarr;與講者進行交流較一段講座為有趣&rarr;獲益更多&rarr;以補習班為例子說明現時同學發問機會少&rarr;所以希望透過活動讓同學知道發問的重要性<br />\n<br />\n問題：無講到熱心發問點有助學習，作者一直指出發問對學習好重要，但無去再說明兩者嘅關係，亦都無緊扣態度重要性落去活動<br />\n<br />\n有時候可能大家覺得自己寫到好多，但其實都係無解釋清楚到你嘅論點嘅存在理由。大家可以參考返同一份pdf第五級示例一，作者有講到熱心發問姐係應該點做（樂於回應＋保持友善&rarr;形成交流答問），再講到熱心發問點樣幫助同學係釋囚人士分享會學到野（令釋囚者打開心屝／直接解答心中問題／放下偏見才能學習到深刻的人生哲理與勸喻）。呢d就係相對完整嘅答案。<br />\n<br />\n所以係睇sample嘅時候，最好係做埋分析，睇下人地一段嘅結構係點樣出黎，再引用返落自己平時作文度，咁就可以大大改善文章嘅邏輯"},{"pid":"e064ba8ab6684ba19eb723ac2b28d4bb16d42b1a","tid":1887643,"uid":296931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:30:25.000Z","msg":"香港文學界又少咗個人了 青少年文學作家君比病逝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894890</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4201ce267fd4aa177219db57bc299280ac971480","tid":1887643,"uid":327953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee867042eabfdc627c5b9b3387d42902670b997","tid":1887643,"uid":138489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"中英作文都5** 中文paper 3 5* 想睇卷可以留TG <br />\n就grad唔收補習 唔收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T19:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20888552acb703f3aa4f01c433eac13e3427e706","tid":1887643,"uid":327953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee867042eabfdc627c5b9b3387d42902670b997","tid":1887643,"uid":138489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"中英作文都5** 中文paper 3 5* 想睇卷可以留TG <br />\n就grad唔收補習 唔收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"我冇左你tg.."}]}